description:
This book is in greek language, so the comments are in same language too.

To biblio poy egrapse o Aggelos Terzakhs gia to Epos tou 1940 - 1941.
Prokeitai gia aristourghma, paroti o idios den htan stratiwtikos kai eixe paei sto Metwpo gia thn dhmosiografikh kalypsh.


Writer: Aggelos Terzakis
Publisher: Geniko Epiteleio Stratou/7o Epiteliko Grafeio
Publication Year: 1990
Edition: 2nd
Pages: 225
Language: Greek
ISBN: -

Skanarismeno se eikones JPEG sta 300dpi.
Oi eikones einai xwrismenes se fakelous ana kefalaio kai exoun onoma ton ari8mo selidas pou antiproswpeuoun.

Oi eikones periexontai mesa sto arxeio CB7. To CB7 einai stin ousia ena arxeio 7z pou aposumpiezetai me to programma 7-zip    &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.7-zip.org/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.7-zip.org/&lt;/a&gt;
Mporei na diabastei opws einai me to programma CDisplayEx    &lt;a href=&quot;
http://sourceforge.net/projects/cdisplayex/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://sourceforge.net/projects/cdisplayex/&lt;/a&gt;


An kapoios 8ewrei oti to mege8os twn skanarismenwn eikonwn einai polu megalo, mporei na katebasei mono to arxeio DjVu.
Ta arxeia DjVu einai eidika gia skanarismena biblia, prokeimenou to mege8os tous na paramenei polu mikro.
Ta arxeia DjVu diabazontai me to programma WinDjView     &lt;a href=&quot;
